<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>hạtqdm wạ̉nạ msẖ kẖạyf</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- (hạtqdm wạ̉nạ msẖ kẖạyf .. mn ḍʿfy wm ạlmjhwl
 ṭwl mạ ạ̉nạ sẖạyfk sẖạyf .. bạlnʿmẗ ạ̹n ạ̉nạ mqbwl)2
 1- (dy mḥbty ạlly bttgẖyr .. wḥbk ạlkbyr
 wdmk ạlly byṭhr .. fy qlby wạlḍmyr)2
 wạ̹ydk ạlly tsnd .. wrwḥk ạlly yrsẖd
 (wṣwtk ạlly yfrd .. sẖrạʿy fy ạlmsyr)2
 2-(wbnwrk qlby ysẖwf .. ạlnwr wyʿysẖ jwạh
 wysẖwf qlbk ʿṭwf .. ʿly̱ jhly bkl mdạh)2
 wṣrt lyã rạʿy .. tạkẖdny fy ạlmrạʿy
 (trdny fy ḍyạʿy .. lrạḥẗ ạlmyạh)2</lyrics>
<hymn_number>1565</hymn_number>
<author>mạhr fạyz, mạhr fạyz</author>
</song>